Answers Link: https://github.com/cnoviello/mastering-stm32/tree/master/nucleo-l476RG/src

Evdeki VirtualComSeriPort örneğinin ayarları:

USB_DEVICE = Class For FS IP -> Communication Device Class
RCC = High Speed Clock -> BYPASS Clock Source
      Low Speed Clock -> Crystal/Ceramic Res..
SYS = Debug -> Serial Wire
      Timebase Source -> Systick 
USART3 = Mode -> Async..
USB_OTG_FS = Mode -> Device Only 
             Activate_SOF ve Activate_VBUS kutucukları  tiklenmiş.
